  "title": "sales manager",
  "description": "<p>Our company is acting on behalf of our client who has good food business . They need experienced sales manager with the following job responsibilities and requirements-</p><p>Supervise the activities of the sales team including marketing activities of the product</p><p>Assist the general manager to run competent sales team.</p><p>Provide reports to top management like sales reports, lead generation reports, customer reports, and new customers reports.</p><p>Prepare sales presentations and other sales tools.</p><p>sales managers to ensure adequate client communication, maintain contacts with clients and provide feedback.</p><p>Initiate sales activities, strategies, and sales plans required to build brand visibility.</p><p>Job highlights</p><p>4 off days monthly, rest days depend on schedule. able to work long hours and late in evenings and weekends</p><p>Competitive salary </p><p>Positive and nurturing working environment</p><p>Work location: co office area</p><p>Duration: permanent</p><p>Requirements</p><p>Qualifications - diploma or high school diploma and degree with good experience</p><p>Work experience- at least one year working experience in related fields</p><p>Job type- full time</p><p>Required languages: English and able to communicate with mandarin speaking customers</p><p>If you have an interest in applying for this role, please WhatsApp me at 98198786 to apply. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Priority will be given to Singaporeans</p><p>Young hon Lim/ manager</p><p>Render private limited</p><p>EA licence no 15c7827</p><p>EA reg no R1550906</p>",
